  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Aim of the study is the definition of criteria for a standardized assessment of heart
      function by 3D echocardiographic procedures. Standardized criteria will be defined to assess
      aortic valve insufficiency after TAVI and success of mitral valve replacement respectively.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
